  "description": "Use when designing wrapper or inner classes in Apex to combine SObjects with computed fields, shape data for LWC consumption, or sort collections with Comparable or Comparator. Trigger keywords: wrapper class, inner class, Comparable, Comparator, @AuraEnabled fields, @JsonAccess. NOT for JSON serialization mechanics \u2014 use apex-json-serialization. NOT for LWC data-binding patterns \u2014 use lwc-reactive-state-patterns or lwc-lightning-record-forms.",
  "file_location": "skills/apex/apex-wrapper-class-patterns",
  "id": "apex/apex-wrapper-class-patterns",
  "inputs": [
    "SObject types and computed/aggregate fields that need to be combined in a single response object",
    "Sort criteria (single or multiple) for a list of wrapper or custom objects",
    "Target consumer: LWC component (needs @AuraEnabled), Apex REST endpoint (needs @JsonAccess), or internal Apex service"
  ],
